1
00:00:09,166 --> 00:00:10,708
Who are you?

2
00:00:10,791 --> 00:00:14,250
I am Casshern.

3
00:00:14,333 --> 00:00:18,291
Luna... I will kill you.

4
00:01:48,500 --> 00:01:50,583
[WHOOSH]

5
00:01:50,666 --> 00:01:52,875
[LOUD THUDS]

6
00:01:52,958 --> 00:01:55,458
[METAL WARRIOR YELLS]

7
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:00,958
[METAL WARRIOR YELLS]

8
00:02:10,208 --> 00:02:13,083
[SHATTERING SOUND]

9
00:02:38,208 --> 00:02:43,625
[BRAIKING BOSS] It all began
on one day... the ruin.

10
00:02:43,708 --> 00:02:45,958
From the moment
he murdered Luna,

11
00:02:46,041 --> 00:02:48,125
our world began to crumble,

12
00:02:48,208 --> 00:02:52,083
and there is nothing
we can do to stop it.

13
00:02:52,166 --> 00:02:53,416
[BRAIKING BOSS LAUGHS]

14
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:54,458
[RUMBLING]

15
00:02:54,541 --> 00:02:56,500
[EXPLOSION]

16
00:02:58,291 --> 00:03:03,250
The one responsible for
her death is Casshern.

17
00:03:03,333 --> 00:03:06,708
Yes, that damned Casshern!

18
00:03:09,333 --> 00:03:13,958
He owes the world a favor
after what he did to it.

19
00:03:17,916 --> 00:03:21,041
[METAL WARRIORS]
Kill Casshern...

20
00:03:21,125 --> 00:03:27,416
Kill Casshern... Kill Casshern.

21
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:34,416
Kill Casshern! Kill Casshern!

22
00:03:38,458 --> 00:03:39,833
[CASSHERN GRUNTS]

23
00:03:42,416 --> 00:03:44,458
[CASSHERN YELLS]

24
00:03:46,208 --> 00:03:48,583
[METAL WARRIOR YELLS]

25
00:03:48,666 --> 00:03:51,041
[CASSHERN YELLS]

26
00:03:53,291 --> 00:03:56,416
[CASSHERN GRUNTS]

27
00:04:12,916 --> 00:04:14,666
[CRACK]

28
00:04:16,916 --> 00:04:20,125
[LYUZE] The one who brought
ruin to this world is named...

29
00:04:20,208 --> 00:04:21,500
...Casshern.

30
00:04:28,583 --> 00:04:30,583
[METAL WARRIOR YELLS]

31
00:04:31,125 --> 00:04:34,333
[LOUD THUDS]

32
00:04:40,458 --> 00:04:43,041
[METAL WARRIOR YELLS]

33
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,125
[METAL WARRIOR H]
Devour Casshern!

34
00:04:46,208 --> 00:04:48,958
[METAL WARRIOR YELLS]

35
00:04:57,041 --> 00:04:58,375
[METAL WARRIOR H] Kill...

36
00:04:58,458 --> 00:05:00,250
[LOUD THUD]

37
00:05:02,083 --> 00:05:05,458
Kill Casshern.

38
00:05:09,458 --> 00:05:13,875
Devour Casshern!

39
00:05:13,958 --> 00:05:17,250
What for...?
How does eating me serve you?

40
00:05:17,333 --> 00:05:18,500
[METAL WARRIOR H LAUGHS]

41
00:05:18,583 --> 00:05:21,291
[METAL WARRIOR H]
The ruin will never stop.

42
00:05:21,375 --> 00:05:23,208
My body couldn't last another

43
00:05:23,291 --> 00:05:26,208
six months in this
state of decay...

44
00:05:26,291 --> 00:05:29,666
...even if you let me
walk away unharmed.

45
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:32,375
And what does that
have to do with me?

46
00:05:32,458 --> 00:05:34,333
[METAL WARRIOR H] Casshern...

47
00:05:34,416 --> 00:05:38,875
If I eat you, I will
attain eternal life.

48
00:05:38,958 --> 00:05:40,750
You're lying!

49
00:05:40,833 --> 00:05:44,333
[METAL WARRIOR H] I have no idea
whether it's true or not, but...

50
00:05:44,416 --> 00:05:46,416
I'm not going to sit around

51
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:49,291
waiting to die without
trying something!

52
00:05:49,375 --> 00:05:51,666
You better believe that!

53
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:57,125
Die!

54
00:05:57,208 --> 00:05:57,916
[CASSHERN YELLS]

55
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:03,083
[PUNCHES LANDING]

56
00:06:13,166 --> 00:06:16,333
The ruin won't stop...

57
00:06:16,416 --> 00:06:20,791
They believe if they eat me
they will live forever.

58
00:06:26,458 --> 00:06:27,250
[WHOOSH]

59
00:06:27,333 --> 00:06:28,708
[THUD]

60
00:06:35,125 --> 00:06:41,166
[LYUZE] Kill Casshern...
Devour Casshern.

61
00:06:41,250 --> 00:06:46,916
Kill Casshern...
Devour Casshern.

62
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:50,458
Destroy Casshern.

63
00:06:50,541 --> 00:06:53,791
[CRUMBLING SOUND]

64
00:06:53,875 --> 00:06:56,958
[LYUZE LAUGHS]

65
00:06:57,041 --> 00:06:58,125
[LYUZE]
They seem to be quite frail

66
00:06:58,208 --> 00:07:01,333
once they've lost
their consciousness.

67
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:18,166
It's such a fragile world...
full of robots...

68
00:07:22,708 --> 00:07:29,541
[CASSHERN GRUNTS IN PAIN]

69
00:07:29,625 --> 00:07:34,375
[CASSHERN YELLS IN PAIN]

70
00:07:34,458 --> 00:07:36,500
[OHJI] Huh...?

71
00:07:46,583 --> 00:07:48,791
Ohji...

72
00:07:51,333 --> 00:07:53,625
Ringo?
What are you awake for?

73
00:07:53,708 --> 00:07:57,166
Why don't you try
to go back to sleep?

74
00:08:00,875 --> 00:08:01,666
[RINGO GIGGLES]

75
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:04,041
[TRUCK STARTS]

76
00:08:21,583 --> 00:08:25,625
[METAL WARRIOR C]
Devour Casshern.

77
00:08:25,708 --> 00:08:28,250
[BRAIKING BOSS] Pinning
your hopes on a rumor... 

78
00:08:28,333 --> 00:08:31,125
What could eating
him actually do? 

79
00:08:31,208 --> 00:08:33,500
It would never be
enough to stop the ruin.

80
00:08:33,583 --> 00:08:36,250
[METAL WARRIOR C]
You... You're that...

81
00:08:36,333 --> 00:08:37,958
[POWERING DOWN]

82
00:08:38,041 --> 00:08:39,208
[SHATTERING]

83
00:08:39,291 --> 00:08:42,541
Yes, the end has
already begun...

84
00:08:42,625 --> 00:08:45,291
But don't forget you are
still obliged to make...

85
00:08:45,375 --> 00:08:49,208
...amends, Casshern.

86
00:08:49,291 --> 00:08:51,833
As are we.

87
00:08:59,250 --> 00:09:03,500
[OHJI THINKING] So Casshern...
You've finally awakened.

88
00:09:06,458 --> 00:09:08,083
[BRAIKING BOSS]
We knew this would happen.

89
00:09:08,166 --> 00:09:12,291
Looks like business is
about to pick up for you.

90
00:09:37,583 --> 00:09:39,583
[RINGO LAUGHS]

91
00:09:44,250 --> 00:09:47,583
[RINGO LAUGHS]

92
00:10:05,333 --> 00:10:09,041
[RINGO LAUGHS]

93
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:26,416
Pretty.

94
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,458
Who me?

95
00:10:27,541 --> 00:10:30,000
[RINGO]
Mm-Hmm.

96
00:10:32,875 --> 00:10:36,250
[RINGO]
Mister, are you human?

97
00:10:37,541 --> 00:10:40,666
So you're a robot?

98
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:44,666
Well... probably.

99
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:47,500
You're not sure?

100
00:10:56,250 --> 00:10:57,833
What's a human?

101
00:10:57,916 --> 00:10:58,875
[RINGO]
I don't know.

102
00:10:58,958 --> 00:11:02,791
I haven't seen very many before.

103
00:11:02,875 --> 00:11:05,500
But... I thought you may
be one of those humans...

104
00:11:05,583 --> 00:11:08,166
...'cause you're so pretty.

105
00:11:11,666 --> 00:11:13,041
What's your
name mister?

106
00:11:13,125 --> 00:11:15,000
You have a name,
don't you?

107
00:11:15,083 --> 00:11:16,541
My name?

108
00:11:16,625 --> 00:11:19,416
My name... is Ringo.

109
00:11:21,583 --> 00:11:25,250
My name is Ringo!

110
00:11:27,541 --> 00:11:29,000
I am...

111
00:11:29,083 --> 00:11:31,791
[METAL WARRIORS]
Kill Casshern...

112
00:11:31,875 --> 00:11:38,041
Kill Casshern... Kill Casshern.

113
00:11:38,125 --> 00:11:40,166
[CASSHERN GRUNTS]

114
00:11:40,250 --> 00:11:42,083
I am Casshern.

115
00:11:42,166 --> 00:11:44,583
Casshern?

116
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:56,416
[RINGO] Aww...!

117
00:12:00,958 --> 00:12:03,166
Hey, I was arranging those!

118
00:12:03,250 --> 00:12:07,541
You're mean...
Mister... Water!

119
00:12:12,291 --> 00:12:12,875
Huh...?

120
00:12:12,958 --> 00:12:14,208
[RINGO GASPS]

121
00:12:14,291 --> 00:12:17,958
[RINGO GIGGLES]

122
00:12:18,041 --> 00:12:20,875
[RINGO GRUNTS]

123
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:25,125
[RINGO LAUGHS]

124
00:12:29,583 --> 00:12:32,500
[RINGO LAUGHS]

125
00:12:34,375 --> 00:12:37,625
[RINGO GIGGLES]

126
00:12:49,291 --> 00:12:53,708
[RINGO GIGGLES]

127
00:12:53,791 --> 00:12:56,250
Are you... a robot too?

128
00:12:56,333 --> 00:12:57,541
[RINGO LAUGHS]

129
00:12:57,625 --> 00:12:59,541
I had started to rust real bad,

130
00:12:59,625 --> 00:13:01,833
but Ohji fixed me right up.

131
00:13:01,916 --> 00:13:03,791
If it weren't for all
that rust earlier,

132
00:13:03,875 --> 00:13:07,083
I bet I'd be much prettier.

133
00:13:09,375 --> 00:13:13,250
But now... the ruin has begun.

134
00:13:21,583 --> 00:13:23,375
So, what is the ruin?

135
00:13:23,458 --> 00:13:26,083
Is it happening to me?

136
00:13:27,208 --> 00:13:29,208
Ooohhh!

137
00:13:29,291 --> 00:13:31,375
I don't get it!

138
00:13:31,458 --> 00:13:34,083
All I know is you're
really pretty, Mister.

139
00:13:34,166 --> 00:13:37,125
You're not all broken down
and corroded like me.

140
00:13:37,208 --> 00:13:40,000
You're more like a human!

141
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:45,125
Well, I better get home...

142
00:13:45,208 --> 00:13:47,666
...before Ohji starts
worrying about me.

143
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:53,333
♪ Ohji is a worry wart!
Sweet Ohji is a worry wart! ♪

144
00:13:53,416 --> 00:13:54,666
Bye-bye!

145
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:56,416
[RINGO LAUGHS]

146
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:58,583
Wait, hold on!

147
00:14:05,625 --> 00:14:09,500
I don't think
you're broken at all.

148
00:14:09,583 --> 00:14:12,458
I think you're beautiful.

149
00:14:20,666 --> 00:14:22,916
Here you can have this...

150
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,833
Of all the shells
I've found so far,

151
00:14:24,916 --> 00:14:27,416
this one's the prettiest.

152
00:14:30,625 --> 00:14:33,083
It's for good luck.

153
00:14:34,416 --> 00:14:36,458
[CASSHERN] Thank you.

154
00:14:40,208 --> 00:14:42,500
No, thank you.

155
00:14:44,958 --> 00:14:46,458
[CASSHERN GASPS]

156
00:14:48,541 --> 00:14:52,833
[FOOTSTEPS]

157
00:14:55,125 --> 00:14:56,708
[CASSHERN GASPS]

158
00:14:59,875 --> 00:15:04,375
[RINGO LAUGHS]

159
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:07,666
[CASSHERN] Was that...

160
00:15:11,333 --> 00:15:13,208
...Luna?

161
00:15:13,291 --> 00:15:16,666
[CLATTERING]

162
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:17,666
Ringo!

163
00:15:17,750 --> 00:15:19,166
[RINGO GASPS]

164
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:20,791
[WHOOSHING]

165
00:15:23,958 --> 00:15:26,666
[METAL WARRIOR I GROWLS]

166
00:15:28,125 --> 00:15:30,833
[METAL WARRIOR I] 
Humans deserve to feel the ruin,

167
00:15:30,916 --> 00:15:33,833
just like us!

168
00:15:33,916 --> 00:15:36,791
But Ringo is a robot.

169
00:15:36,875 --> 00:15:40,541
[METAL WARRIOR I] 
A robotic brat? I hate brats!

170
00:15:40,625 --> 00:15:44,458
I can't stand
their foul stench!

171
00:15:44,541 --> 00:15:45,708
Uhh...

172
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:51,208
[CLATTERING]

173
00:15:51,291 --> 00:15:53,708
[METAL WARRIOR I] The world
is heading towards ruin.

174
00:15:53,791 --> 00:15:58,375
There will be no
place for brats like you.

175
00:15:58,458 --> 00:16:00,458
Now die.

176
00:16:00,541 --> 00:16:01,625
[CRACKING]

177
00:16:01,708 --> 00:16:02,583
[LOUD THUDS]

178
00:16:02,666 --> 00:16:04,333
[METAL WARRIOR I GRUNTS]

179
00:16:04,416 --> 00:16:05,041
[CASSHERN YELLS]

180
00:16:05,125 --> 00:16:07,208
[METAL WARRIOR I YELLS]

181
00:16:12,791 --> 00:16:15,083
Let her go... Walk away.

182
00:16:15,166 --> 00:16:17,541
[METAL WARRIOR I]
Who do you think you are?

183
00:16:17,625 --> 00:16:20,208
Drop her.

184
00:16:20,291 --> 00:16:22,958
[METAL WARRIOR I]
Wait... Are you...?

185
00:16:27,500 --> 00:16:29,541
Ringo.

186
00:16:37,458 --> 00:16:40,750
So pretty... Heh.

187
00:16:47,708 --> 00:16:49,250
Hey there, Mister.

188
00:16:49,333 --> 00:16:51,250
[RINGO LAUGHS LIGHTLY]

189
00:16:53,291 --> 00:16:56,750
[LOUD FOOTSTEPS]

190
00:17:00,625 --> 00:17:02,583
[METAL WARRIOR I]
Now I know who you are...

191
00:17:02,666 --> 00:17:04,708
You're Casshern!

192
00:17:04,791 --> 00:17:06,041
I hear that if I eat you,

193
00:17:06,125 --> 00:17:08,958
it will stop the ruin
from advancing...

194
00:17:09,041 --> 00:17:13,416
I don't believe for
a second that it's true.

195
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:15,541
But I do understand why others

196
00:17:15,625 --> 00:17:19,125
would want to
believe such a lie.

197
00:17:19,208 --> 00:17:26,041
I've never seen such a new
body before... so pristine.

198
00:17:31,333 --> 00:17:36,458
It won't be for much longer...
not after I crush it!

199
00:17:38,958 --> 00:17:41,791
What the... What was that?!

200
00:17:47,416 --> 00:17:49,333
[METAL WARRIOR I YELLS]

201
00:17:53,833 --> 00:17:55,833
[METAL WARRIOR I YELLS]

202
00:18:02,958 --> 00:18:06,125
[FIGHTING SOUNDS]

203
00:18:27,875 --> 00:18:31,291
[METAL WARRIOR I SCREAMS]

204
00:18:38,666 --> 00:18:40,875
Careful Mister.

205
00:18:49,875 --> 00:18:52,375
[METAL WARRIOR I]
Stop, please!

206
00:18:52,458 --> 00:18:54,708
No, wait.

207
00:18:54,791 --> 00:18:57,458
[METAL WARRIOR I YELLS]

208
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:12,375
[METAL WARRIOR I SCREAMS]

209
00:19:12,458 --> 00:19:15,041
[CLATTERING]

210
00:19:24,375 --> 00:19:26,791
[METAL WARRIOR I]
I don't want to die.

211
00:19:26,875 --> 00:19:30,083
[CRUMBLING]

212
00:19:36,416 --> 00:19:37,958
Huh...

213
00:20:01,291 --> 00:20:04,000
[TRUCK APPROACHING]

214
00:20:06,458 --> 00:20:07,541
Ohji!

215
00:20:07,625 --> 00:20:09,208
[CLATTERING]

216
00:20:13,416 --> 00:20:16,000
[OHJI]
Please stay where you are.

217
00:20:18,625 --> 00:20:22,708
Seeing you...
I can hardly believe it.

218
00:20:22,791 --> 00:20:24,666
[RINGO CRIES]

219
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:28,833
[TRUCK STARTS]

220
00:20:39,708 --> 00:20:42,083
[CRUMBLING SOUND]

221
00:20:42,166 --> 00:20:46,708
[LYUZE] She's upset because she
doesn't want to leave your side.

222
00:20:49,416 --> 00:20:50,625
As I thought...

223
00:20:50,708 --> 00:20:53,875
Your true nature has
come to light today.

224
00:20:56,833 --> 00:21:01,083
The ease at which you
kill is impressive... yet...

225
00:21:01,166 --> 00:21:03,791
...you're the worst thing
to happen to this world.

226
00:21:03,875 --> 00:21:05,791
You're despicable.

227
00:21:05,875 --> 00:21:09,375
You know about me...?
Please tell me.

228
00:21:16,666 --> 00:21:19,750
I know enough about you
to want to kill you for it.

229
00:21:19,833 --> 00:21:21,291
Then come
out with it...

230
00:21:21,375 --> 00:21:24,041
Just what am I?

231
00:21:24,125 --> 00:21:27,416
Casshern...
You are a killing machine.

232
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:28,750
You see...

233
00:21:28,833 --> 00:21:31,041
You took the life of the
Sun that was named Moon...

234
00:21:31,125 --> 00:21:34,291
...and because of that,
the ruin began.

235
00:21:35,583 --> 00:21:37,541
[CRUMBLING SOUND]

236
00:21:38,916 --> 00:21:43,375
And now...
the world... is dead.

237
00:21:44,208 --> 00:21:47,041
[CLATTERING]

238
00:21:53,083 --> 00:21:54,541
[CASSHERN THINKING]
I know nothing...

239
00:21:54,625 --> 00:21:56,750
...not even myself...

240
00:21:56,833 --> 00:22:01,375
Yet my enemies
call me... Casshern.

241
00:23:34,375 --> 00:23:36,291
[CASSHERN]
There was a commune of robots

242
00:23:36,375 --> 00:23:39,833
who accepted
death as their fate.

243
00:23:39,916 --> 00:23:41,125
Next time...

244
00:23:41,208 --> 00:23:44,875
A World Replete
with Death Throes.

